name: Gemini Llamas
description: The Gemini Llama twins are like yin and yang. One is a total socialite and loves to have fun, and the other keeps the pair grounded by ensuring their starflower shop’s spreadsheet is always up-to-date. Together they make one versatile unit that can pull together the BEST New Year’s party, as long as you can handle not knowing whether it’s time to have fun or get serious.
